GObject introspection library for ALSA userspace library

Requirements:
- Linux with ALSA
- alsa-lib
- autoconf
- automake
- glib-2.0
- gobject-2.0

How to build:
 $ ./autogen.sh
 $ ./configure
 $ make
 $ make install

How to test:
 (needless to install)
 $ ./autogen.sh
 $ ./configure
 $ make
 $ ./sample/run.sh [ctl|timer|seq]
 (PyGObject is required.)

Current status:
 Under development.
 - Partly support for Control interface
 - Partly support for Timer interface
 - Partly support for Sequencer interface
